title: The Women's Fitness Book (gnv64)
description:
The Women's Fitness Book
by DK Publishing
DK ADULT | January 2012 | ISBN-10: 0756689643 | True PDF | 336 pages | 32.2 mb

The Women's Fitness Book is like having a personal trainer in the palm of your hand. It includes advice on healthy eating and weight loss; tips on motivation, setting goals, and nutrition; instruction on how to establish and maintain fitness levels; and questionnaires and tests to accurately assess readers' starting point and progress.
The Women's Fitness Book is a comprehensive tool, providing everything necessary for women to get healthy, sculpt the body they want, and maintain that healthy body for life.

Workouts include:
-  Skinny Jeans Workout
-  Amazing Abs Workout
-  Lunch Break Workout
-  Five Minute Workout
